{"tid":1453994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門冰室羅生門？","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:45.000Z","uid":154004,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"656d073a0c7079976158191529351cd187614939","tid":1453994,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"事緣富臨集團旗下係有 龍門冰室<br />\n依家呢個時勢 比人罷佢老母<br />\n<br />\n今日龍門冰室fb page就走出嚟話：<br />\n佢地同屯門海麗、香港仔分店 無關<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkw8g5z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjkw8g5z.png&h=37855967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話會考慮改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSpNxD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSpNxD7.png&h=23bc1ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但睇返佢哋official IG :<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明之前仲一團和氣話開咗分店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zu7LjjE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZu7LjjE.png&h=a8d265fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYoKzS0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYoKzS0.png&h=48260a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n合理推測：本身傾掂係分店，想搞大佢，但依家富臨出咗事就割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續罷佢老母 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信佢哋無關係"},{"pid":"8e850f6696c355b69c19452be0a94c49cbfaf363","tid":1453994,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLEooS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLEooS.png&h=4b443cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i